    <h1>Orphaned Page</h1>
    <p class="description">A webpage that exists on a website but has <strong>no internal links pointing to it</strong>. Users cannot reach it through normal navigation, and Googlebot may never crawl it — leaving content invisible to search engines despite being live on the server.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
